text.section:
Any public body issuing bonds under this section shall approve and make available to purchasers of these bonds an official statement or other disclosure document that shall include, without limitation, the following:
A description of the security for the bonds;
A statement of the purposes for which the proceeds of the bonds will be used;
A description of the financial condition of the public body issuing the bonds;
The price or prices for the interest rate or rates to be paid on the bonds; and
A statement of the time or times and place or places of payment of the principal of and interest on the bonds.
